918
00:46:29.750 --> 00:46:32.119
Kenapa dia baik-baik saja?

919
00:46:32.719 --> 00:46:33.989
Bedebah yang gigih.

920
00:46:35.320 --> 00:46:36.559
Du Shik.

921
00:46:36.760 --> 00:46:38.989
Sudah berapa banyak yang kita selesaikan?

922
00:46:38.989 --> 00:46:40.429
