924
00:46:43.000 --> 00:46:44.030
Kita lihat?

925
00:46:48.300 --> 00:46:51.210
Apa? Masih tersisa banyak.

926
00:46:51.369 --> 00:46:52.469
Celaka.

927
00:46:52.539 --> 00:46:54.079
Astaga.

928
00:46:54.079 --> 00:46:56.239
Kapan kita akan menyelesaikan ini?

929
00:46:56.239 --> 00:46:57.780
Aku sangat lelah.

930
00:47:04.090 --> 00:47:05.320
Du Shik.

931
00:47:05.619 --> 00:47:08.119
Aku jelas bisa melanjutkan,

932
00:47:08.519 --> 00:47:11.860
